title: Oregon Geospatial Enterprise Office, Lakes - 303d, Oregon, 2002
name: Oregon Geospatial Enterprise Office, Lakes - 303d, Oregon, 2002
description:
This polygon theme contains a spatial representation of the 303(d) list and should be used in conjunction with the actual 303(d) list. The 303(d) list attribute information included in the GIS attributes table is generalized and is described below. 
Purpose:
    This layer was developed in order to portray spatially some elements of the 303(d) list and to assist in the 303(d) list development process

author.source: Department of Environmental Quality; Oregon Geospatial Enterprise Office
